ufw allow from 192.168.99.0/24 to any port 22

ufw allow proto tcp from any to any port 49153:49193




# vpnの設定
## vpsでufwを利用して､dnsサーバーとかとして利用｡
https://libreddit.kavin.rocks/r/WireGuard/comments/ik6w4h/etcdefaultufw_default_forward_policyaccept/

In the wg0-up script:

ufw route allow in on wg0 out on eth0
ufw route allow in on eth0 out on wg0

In the wg0-down script:

ufw route delete allow in on wg0 out on eth0
ufw route delete allow in on eth0 out on wg0

ポート53を開くか､routingの設定が必要そう

Without masquerade, you're routing tables on the LAN will need to know where to send the packets for the wireguard network.
Also, you need routing enabled in sysctl.conf:
net.ipv4.ip_forward = 1
